### Match Data Tests

### 1. Matches ReadList (Legacy) - Get matches in a division
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/Matches.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byDivisionID&divisionID={{testDivisionID}}

### 2. Matches ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/matches/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "divisionID": {{testDivisionID}}
}

### 3. MatchTeams ReadList (Legacy) - Get teams in a match
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/MatchTeams.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byMatchID&matchID=1

### 4. MatchTeams ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/match-teams/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchID": 1
}

### 5. RealMatches ReadList (Legacy) - Get real football matches
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/RealMatches.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byCompetition&realCompetitionID={{testRealCompetitionID}}&realCompetitionMatchDay={{testRealCompetitionMatchDay}}

### 6. RealMatches ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/real-matches/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realCompetitionID": {{testRealCompetitionID}},
  "realCompetitionMatchDay": {{testRealCompetitionMatchDay}}
}

### 7. RealMatches ReadList - Filter by SYMID and MatchDay
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/RealMatches.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byCompetition&realCompetitionSYMID=EN_PR&realCompetitionMatchDay=5
